description: Lixiang Education Holding Co., Ltd., through its subsidiaries, provides high school education and vocational education in the People's Republic of China. It also engages in the operation of food procurement and information technology development businesses. The company was formerly known as Lianwai Education Group Limited and changed its name to Lixiang Education Holding Co., Ltd. in May 2020. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Lishui, the People's Republic of China.
